metadata.name: Thematical Accuracy
metadata.description:
The following report assesses the thematic accuracy of object descriptions in the selected region.


                            The quality attribute "Thematic Accuracy" estimates how precise the description of the objects is.

result.description: The report indicates good thematical_accuracy of the underlying OSM data.
result.label: green

metadata.name: Tags Ratio
metadata.description:
Derive the ratio of OSM features compared to features which
match additional expected tags (e.g. amenity=hospital vs
amenity=hospital and wheelchair=yes).

layer.name: Building Count
layer.description: All buildings as defined by all objects tagged with 'building=*'.

result.description:
The ratio of the features (all: 87527.0) compared to features with
expected tags (matched: 37767.0) is 0.4.
